{"tid":1824330,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍田連儂牆「撕紙」兼鎚襲青年ㅤ中年漢認罪　法官：必判監","createTime":"2020-01-14T10:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T11:16:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7568bcba27f100f3df9432851b6aaea21fc37f","tid":1824330,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"中年男地盤工於去年 8 月中凌晨，在藍田啟田商場外的連儂牆撕紙，並與在場人士爭執，期間以鎚仔襲擊一名青年，撕紙的地盤工今（14日）於觀塘裁判法院承認傷人及管有攻擊性武器兩罪。署理主任裁判官徐綺薇指， 不應因政見不同而傷人，因本案性質嚴重，明言「必須會判處監禁」，將案押後至 2 月 4 日判刑，期間為被告索取背景報告。<br />\n<br />\n被告有兩項案底，辯方求情時指， 近大半年有很多人也受社會氣氛影響， 暴力不應被容許，法庭亦不應考慮政治因素。辯方指被告當晚與朋友吃飯，曾飲酒，回家途經現場，與人爭執，魯莽下才會犯事，涉案鎚仔為其平日隨身攜帶的物品，被告並非有預謀犯案。<br />\n<br />\n辯方提議為被告索取社會服務令報告，遭徐官拒絕，表明不會考慮社會服務令，直言會判處即時監禁。<br />\n<br />\n蔡今承認「傷人 19」的傷人罪及管有攻擊性武器罪，指於去年 8 月 15 日在藍田啟田商場外非法及惡意傷害湯姓男子及管有一把鎚。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年 8 月 15 日約凌晨 3 時，被告將藍田啟田商場外的連儂牆上的文宣撕下，並與在場的 4 名男子發生爭執 ，被告其隨身膠袋中取出一把鎚施襲，擊中其一名湯姓男子的上唇，其餘三人報警，被告其後在廣田苑外被捕，在警誡下承認傷人。湯姓事主被送往聯合醫院治理，上唇須縫兩針。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%97%8D%E7%94%B0%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-%E6%92%95%E7%B4%99-%E5%85%BC%E9%8E%9A%E8%A5%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E1%85%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E5%BF%85%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%2594%25B0%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586-%25E6%2592%2595%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E5%2585%25BC%25E9%258E%259A%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E1%2585%25A0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%259B%25A3%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=be12338b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%2594%25B0%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586-%25E6%2592%2595%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E5%2585%25BC%25E9%258E%259A%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E1%2585%25A0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%259B%25A3%2F&h=0a11ef5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%97%8D%E7%94%B0%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-%E6%92%95%E7%B4%99-%E5%85%BC%E9%8E%9A%E8%A5%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E1%85%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E5%BF%85%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3/</a>"},{"pid":"2a9cbb4caba47a15bcaa4f1c3f05eb5d516b701c","tid":1824330,"uid":93383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"被告有兩項案底<br />\n<br />\n反社會少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045a476bd7c7559d1870409d065300e6bad991e1","tid":1824330,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想救連登，試下依個方法</span><br />\n<br />\n【測試】熱門新功能&mdash;行動篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824310</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7addd9f36f3a426c0eb589e3f59e57fd3ba1fe3b","tid":1824330,"uid":215113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"咁又唔洗告盜竊呀"},{"pid":"1de6314c572f9531ac5a6e2e106f605de6229545","tid":1824330,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>涉案鎚仔為其平日隨身攜帶的物品，被告並非有預謀犯案</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"77763784d7330b5cbbaf4a9acb1eeb6130bd94f8","tid":1824330,"uid":55043,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"原來可以隨身帶鎚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲真係大撚曬"},{"pid":"e8204974fa01cec7c17f675d6b02fd5defb1dc08","tid":1824330,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"